These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, horror, animation
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, chaman, vegafina
3 different games are played: bridge, canasta, domino
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, aquamarine, pink
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, april
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, bus
 1. the person driving the boat is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person driving the bus is the mechanic##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person watching horror movies##2
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 5. the designer is the vegafina-smoker##1
 6. the person playing domino is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 8. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 9. the person driving the boat is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person playing canasta is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Movie-Genre      | horror    | animation   | crime           |
| Cigar          | chaman       | vegafina    | bolivar         |
| Game         | canasta    | domino  | bridge        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Color   | aquamarine        | pink    | white       |
| Birthday   | november     | february  | april       |
| Transport         | boat     | jet-ski | bus |

