The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, march, november
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, entrepreneur, coach
City: berlin, venice, liverpool
 1. the coach is the british##1
 2. the coach is the person playing mah-jongg##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the teacher##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is between the person driving the van and the person driving the motorbike##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the van is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the fonseca-smoker is the person playing scrabble##1
 9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
10. the coach is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Transport      | motorbike   | car    | van         |
| Cigar          | fonseca    | dannemann | bongani          |
| Game   | scrabble  | mah-jongg  | snooker     |
