.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
City: miami, rome, hannover
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, magic-tricks, skydiving
There are 3 different favourite colors: green, ebony, purple
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, milk, almond-milk
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, roller, trike
3 different games are played: bridge, poker, mah-jongg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, prince, bolivar
 1. the person traveling to rome is the person playing poker##1
 2. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person who likes green is the person traveling to hannover##1
 4. the person who likes ebony is the person playing poker##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the bolivar-smoker##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person driving the roller and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 8. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
10. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person traveling to hannover##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| City          | hannover      | rome      | miami      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
| Color   | green | ebony    | purple          |
| Beverage   | milk       | mirinda      | almond-milk          |
| Transport   | roller    | skateboard  | trike      |
| Game           | bridge   | poker  | mah-jongg        |
| Cigar         | swisher  | prince   | bolivar     |

