The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris, bellflower
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, november
 1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person driving the helicopter is the person who growsbellflower##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person playing bridge is between the person who likes azure and the person driving the helicopter##2
 6. the person driving the van is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 7. the person playing bridge is the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the musician is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 9. the person driving the van is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
