.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta, tea
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, whist, go
City: rome, edinburgh, berlin
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, may, june
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, zinnia, iris
House: cape-cod, colonial, victorian
There 3 different types of food: pepper, lettuce, avocado
 1. the victorian house is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
 4. the person playing go is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 7. the person eating avocado is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 8. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person eating pepper##1
10. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
11. the person eating pepper is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Game         | mah-jongg     | whist     | go  |
| City   | berlin | rome  | edinburgh |
| Birthday   | may  | june     | april |
| Flower           | balloon-flower        | iris | zinnia     |
| House         | cape-cod    | victorian | colonial   |
| Food     | lettuce        | avocado        | pepper   |

