.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, mah-jongg
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, german, nigerian
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: d&b, disco, rock
City: london, miami, hannover
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, backgammonsy, rose
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, december, february
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the nigerian##1
3. the german is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is between the person who growssunflower and the person traveling to miami##2
5. the nigerian is between the person traveling to hannover and the fan of rock##2
6. the fan of disco is on the right of the nigerian##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
9. the person who growsbackgammonsy is on the left of the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Game      | backgammon      | bridge      | mah-jongg       |
| Nationality          | german      | nigerian    | egyptian   |
| Music-Genre         | rock    | d&b     | disco     |
| City           | miami    | london | hannover   |
| Flower   | backgammonsy    | rose    | sunflower       |
| Birthday         | february | october      | december    |
| Transport     | ship       | helicopter | skateboard |

