.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
City: rome, nizza, boston
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, peach, zucchini
3 different pets are kept: dog, rabbit, rat
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, june, september
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, brown, turquise
House: ranch-style, cottage, townhouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, fisherman
1. the dressmaker is the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
3. the townhouse house is on the right of the cottage house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fisherman##1
5. the person eating peach is between the person traveling to boston and the owner of the dog##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
7. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person who likes brown##1
8. the coach is the person who's birthday is in september##1
9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| City      | boston       | rome     | nizza         |
| Food          | lettuce     | peach      | zucchini     |
| Pet         | rabbit | rat    | dog      |
| Birthday   | april   | june | september    |
| Color   | brown        | turquise     | emerald   |
| House         | ranch-style     | cottage | townhouse |
| Job     | dressmaker     | fisherman       | coach    |

