.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: backgammon, bridge, whist
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, december, april
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, martial-arts
The people have 3 different hobbies: photography, board-games, singing
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, dunhill, blend
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, r&b, blues
1. the person playing backgammon is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the fan of blues is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person watching drama movies is between the person playing whist and the blend-smoker##2
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the fan of blues##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person watching horror movies is the person who's birthday is in march##1
8. the blend-smoker is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
9. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's birthday is in march and the fan of country##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | bridge    | backgammon       | whist      |
| Birthday          | march   | april   | december  |
| Movie-Genre           | horror  | drama | martial-arts    |
| Hobby   | photography   | board-games     | singing  |
| Cigar           | blend     | bluemaster        | dunhill |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| Music-Genre     | r&b    | blues     | country      |

 